         "id": "SECTION_images",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Images from British Museum\n\nThese images are copyright for British Museum and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPhoenician\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPhoenician', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Phoenician text displayed in the British Museum. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite0> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBanner\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBanner', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Banner in a style similar to that found in Wu Zetian's (武則天) tomb. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite1>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgAtra\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAtra', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Babilonia Tablet Babilónico about the flood. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite2>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBuda\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBuda', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">The Flood Tablet. © Trustees of the British Museum ().</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">5 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBritishMuseum0\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBritishMuseum0', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Oblong basket of woven reed. © Trustees of the British Museum (). Shared under a <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)</a>.</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">6 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgGilgamesh\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGilgamesh', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Abydos King List. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite3>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">7 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgMid001\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMid001', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Different types of vessels, exhibited at the British Museum. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite4> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">8 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgEgypt\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgEgypt', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Cyrus Cylinder. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite5> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">9 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPottery1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPottery1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Map of the Inhabited World. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite6>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">10 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgCylinder\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgCylinder', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Tablet found in Tell Al-'Ubaid. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite7>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">11 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgB\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgB', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Astrolabe showing a calendar with the months in Latin, held in the British Museum. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite8> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">12 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgT1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgT1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Tang Dynasty coin from the year <htdate0>, at the British Museum. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite9> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">13 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgAstro\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAstro', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"><i>Epic of Lugalbanda</i>. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite10>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">14 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgCoin\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgCoin', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Clay tablet with materials for Magan boats. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite11>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">15 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgLugalbanda\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgLugalbanda', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Dedicatory cone. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite12>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">16 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgMagan\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMagan', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Glass Beads. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite13>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">17 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgCD\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgCD', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Cylinder Seal of <i>Meskalamdug</i>. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite14>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">18 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgGB\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGB', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Vessel decorated with cord marks, exhibited at the British Museum. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite15> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">19 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgSuanpan\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgSuanpan', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Clovis point projectile exhibited at the British Museum. © Trustees of the British Museum ( ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">20 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgC1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgC1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Arrowhead made from bone, featuring inscriptions. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite16> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">21 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBritishMuseum1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBritishMuseum1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Prism from Library of Ashurbanipal. © Trustees of the British Museum ().</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">22 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPottery\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPottery', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">23 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPoint\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPoint', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">24 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgXuanzong\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgXuanzong', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">25 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgChinese\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgChinese', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">26 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPBM\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPBM', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
